    <item>
      <title>克里姆林宫在欧洲东翼发起混合战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/kremlin-is-advancing-in-hybrid-war-on-europe-s-eastern-flank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲领导人越来越担心，该地区东部边缘地区的一系列投票将考验该地区数十年来走向西方一体化的进程，以及弗拉基米尔·普京长期以来阻止这一进程的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/kremlin-is-advancing-in-hybrid-war-on-europe-s-eastern-flank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
