    <item>
      <title>钻石资源丰富的博茨瓦纳将延长执政党 58 年的执政时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/botswana-elections-ruling-party-set-to-extend-58-year-hold-on-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博茨瓦纳执政党准备在周三的选举中延长对这个钻石​​资源丰富的南部非洲国家近六十年的统治，并确保总统莫克维齐·马西西获得第二个五年任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/botswana-elections-ruling-party-set-to-extend-58-year-hold-on-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯对外国直接投资持乐观态度，因为 2030 年目标仍然遥远</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/saudi-arabia-upbeat-on-fdi-as-2030-goal-remains-distant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯认为近期外国直接投资的趋势正朝着正确的方向发展，同时也承认，沙特要实现 2030 年每年吸引 1000 亿美元的目标还有很长的路要走。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/saudi-arabia-upbeat-on-fdi-as-2030-goal-remains-distant</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 04:37:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
